OL,6,FStation Commander Ryan Hall says:
OL,7,F"This gives us vital information when
OL,8,Fwe arrive about the challenges we may
OL,9,Fface, along with information about
OL,10,Fhydrants, access to the buildings,
OL,11,Fwhere we get water and floor plans."
OL,13,FTo log the information, firefighters
OL,14,Fare visiting high-rise buildings where
OL,15,Feverything is recorded on an iPad and
OL,16,Fstored on a central computer.
