OL,6,FJersey firefighter Georgina Connor
OL,7,Fexplains: "We're looking at how many
OL,8,Ffloors, how wide, how deep and then we
OL,9,Fcan check where the hydrant is and
OL,10,Fwhere we are going to get our water
OL,11,Ffrom because that's key."
OL,13,FProperty manager Charlie Smith
OL,14,Fbelieves the owners of these complexes
OL,15,Falso have an important role in the
OL,16,Fapp's success.
OL,18,FHe says: "The information we provide
OL,19,Fis the layouts of each development.
